libshapedraw.internal

Class ReadonlyVector3PropertyInterpolator

  • java.lang.Object
    • libshapedraw.internal.ReadonlyVector3PropertyInterpolator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyInterpolator<ReadonlyVector3>

    public class ReadonlyVector3PropertyInterpolator
extends java.lang.Object
implements PropertyInterpolator<ReadonlyVector3>
    Internal class. Allows fields of type Vector3/ReadonlyVector3 to be easily animated using Trident.

    Note that the vector object will be reinstantiated each tick. If this is not the desired behavior, animate the vector's individual components instead.

    See Also:
    Animates
